io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.extractor

Class ExtractionSetting

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.extractor.ExtractionSetting
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExtractionConfiguration

    public class ExtractionSetting
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExtractionConfiguration
    A class full of audio properties to specify the properties of an audio file. It is used eventually in JAVE2 while audio conversion is taking place. Strongly recommended to research each of these properties first or else you might make someone deaf!
